            "title": "Mitsubishi Electric partners with ITRI and TTL Jhunan Brewery in Taiwan for CO2 capture tests in a beer production line.",
            "id": "069b20a6-cf5e-4beb-bc9a-9f25e326218b",
            "description": "In Tokyo, Mitsubishi Electric Corporation (TOKYO: 6503) has recently confirmed a collaboration agreement with both the Industrial Technology Research Institute (ITRI) and the Taiwan Tobacco & Liquor Corporation (TTL) Jhunan Brewery. The agreement focuses on conducting demonstration trials related to the capturing and utilization of CO2. Through this collaborative effort, Mitsubishi Electric, ITRI, and TTL aim to capture CO2 emissions from TTL Jhunan Brewery and subsequently refine it for application in a beer production process. This innovative initiative highlights the commitment to sustainability and environmental responsibility in business operations.",
